1. Definitions
“Software” means the source code, build scripts, and documentation in this repository.
“Official Build Artifacts” means prebuilt ISOs, packages, update repositories, keys, and images released by Nithron.
“Non-Commercial Use” means use by an individual for personal, educational, research, or open-source contribution purposes, with no direct or indirect monetary compensation, fee, or other consideration and not on behalf of any for-profit entity.
“Commercial Use” means any use that is not Non-Commercial Use, including use by or on behalf of a for-profit entity, providing services to third parties, hosting, resale, or any monetized distribution.
“Trademarks” means the names “Nithron”, “NithronOS”, “nOS”, related logos, wordmarks, domain names, and other brand assets.

